comments: Nurkic (PHX) is moving alongside of Monk's (SAC) path to the basket when marginal contact occurs between the two players.
Booker (PHX) retreats in Fox's (SAC) path and when he reaches in, there is marginal contact with Fox's leg.
Sabonis (SAC) establishes a position in Nurkic's (PHX) path before engaging.
Fox's (SAC) momentum carries him into Nurkic (PHX), who is in his obtained position and does not initiate the contact as Fox returns to the floor.
Sabonis (SAC) extends his hands slightly into Booker (PHX) as he releases away to roll to the basket.
Booker (PHX) is drawn into the air on the pump fake towards Sabonis (SAC), but the resulting contact is marginal and does not affect Sabonis's ability to enter his shooting motion.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Allen (PHX).
Murray (SAC) grabs and pulls Booker's (PHX) jersey away from his body and the contact affects his FOM during the throw-in.
Sabonis (SAC) reaches in and initiates illegal contact with Booker's (PHX) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Booker (PHX).
Barnes (SAC) commits a take foul on Allen (PHX).
